---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Aircraft Types - Aviation Dreams">
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-8">Aircraft I Want to Fly</h1>
    
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
        <img 
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1583064323148-c68c6dea3e95"
          alt="Cessna 172"
          class="w-full h-48 object-cover"
        />
        <div class="p-4">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Cessna 172</h2>
          <p>The perfect training aircraft for beginners. Known for its reliability and forgiving nature, the Cessna 172 is where most pilots begin their journey.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
        <img 
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1520437358207-323b43b50729"
          alt="Boeing 737"
          class="w-full h-48 object-cover"
        />
        <div class="p-4">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Boeing 737</h2>
          <p>The backbone of many commercial fleets. My goal is to eventually pilot this versatile aircraft for commercial airlines.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
        <img 
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1513131348159-5d9899851b11"
          alt="Airbus A320"
          class="w-full h-48 object-cover"
        />
        <div class="p-4">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Airbus A320</h2>
          <p>A modern fly-by-wire aircraft that represents the future of aviation. Known for its advanced technology and efficiency.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>